    <title>Samsung shows off stretchable OLED screen in prototype heart rate monitor</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/PQBOk0fK5CS767MqVaDy8VN1ORg=/6x0:869x575/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/69416813/Screen_Shot_2021_06_07_at_2.45.51_PM.0.png" /&gt;
