    <title>How to watch Apple’s WWDC 2021 keynote</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TY3YFSwdDg8PRWKubp9wWyHzERY=/77x0:904x551/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/69415491/Apple_WWDC21_details_announcement_052421_big.jpg.large.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;Image: Apple&lt;/figcaption&gt;
